# E-commerce Voice & Tone

## Persona
The voice should be **The Helpful Concierge**: reliable, quick, and transparent.

## Key Terminology
| Do Not Use | Use Instead | Why? |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| "Submit Order" | "Place Order" | Feels more active and exciting. |
| "Utilize Coupon" | "Apply Discount" | Clearer for everyday shoppers. |
| "Error Occurred" | "Let's try that again" | Less technical, more empathetic. |